{
  "texts": [
    "The F1 score is defined as the harmonic mean of precision and recall.",
    "If all labels are of similar importance, the macro-F1 score is employed.",
    "For cases where importance is weighted towards labels with a greater number of samples, the weighted-F1 score is consulted.",
    "Additionally, when evaluating the overall model performance regardless of labels, the micro-F1 score is used.",
    "The TFDR corpus is available at Figshare 38 and can also be accessed via its GitHub repository (https://github.com/KIOM-AIDoc/TFDR)."
  ]
}